    {
      "id": "xHKPRXNHxCaf5FFhvscBJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1193.1353619148795,
      "y": 1812.9198139356529,
      "width": 516.5195922851562,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0o",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1517675456,
      "version": 431,
      "versionNonce": 624287808,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776357730142,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Estimate Storrage Requirements:\n1 B user, 100 msgs/per day --> 100 B Messages/day.\nconcent cap -> can be capped at 1kb.\n1 kb / message = 100Bkb 100Tera bytes * 3o days.\nMost Messages are gonna be delived and removed.\nso database would be need some Terabyte of space.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Estimate Storrage Requirements:\n1 B user, 100 msgs/per day --> 100 B Messages/day.\nconcent cap -> can be capped at 1kb.\n1 kb / message = 100Bkb 100Tera bytes * 3o days.\nMost Messages are gonna be delived and removed.\nso database would be need some Terabyte of space.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "RSwV5qj3luxMrwojPj4_0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1351.9930860592242,
      "y": 1599.8529426558912,
      "width": 90.99992370605469,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1849800768,
      "version": 59,
      "versionNonce": 379250752,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776357888638,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Clinet\n- userId\n- clientId",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Clinet\n- userId\n- clientId",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "wITCcn6VOSsBggTCV5qpm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1177.9932081295365,
      "y": 2032.2528449996412,
      "width": 562.3995971679688,
      "height": 400,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0r",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2060904512,
      "version": 717,
      "versionNonce": 214823872,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776358487314,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "For managing multiple device per client:\n\n- We have a \"client\" table to keep track of a user\nacross all clinets he is logged in.\n- Changes:\n    1. Our Indox will have recipientClinet Id.\n    2. Redis Pub/sub topics will be on clinet.\n- Flow:\n  1. When a client send message -> it gonna look up for\n    the participants.\n  2. For each participants it will fetch all of their clients.\n  3. then send messages to each of them. \n\nThis would increase the rows of inbox table.\n\nSol: It's better to limit the device count for each users.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "For managing multiple device per client:\n\n- We have a \"client\" table to keep track of a user\nacross all clinets he is logged in.\n- Changes:\n    1. Our Indox will have recipientClinet Id.\n    2. Redis Pub/sub topics will be on clinet.\n- Flow:\n  1. When a client send message -> it gonna look up for\n    the participants.\n  2. For each participants it will fetch all of their clients.\n  3. then send messages to each of them. \n\nThis would increase the rows of inbox table.\n\nSol: It's better to limit the device count for each users.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aVF9JTZmh0lZjnf0f2sof",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1171.1931593014115,
      "y": 2493.0529243453443,
      "width": 579.0596923828125,
      "height": 425,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0s",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2060392512,
      "version": 439,
      "versionNonce": 856906688,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776358685985,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Presencse indicator / To show Status of users:\n\nSol:\n    Polling Fashion:\n    - Keeping a table to see if a user is connected or not ! \n    - Query that table to see if a user is active or not !\n    - Flow:\n       When a connection is established with a client server,\n        It writes to a new table \n\n        Available:\n        - userId\n        - status : available | un-available.\n\n    -   \n\n     ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Presencse indicator / To show Status of users:\n\nSol:\n    Polling Fashion:\n    - Keeping a table to see if a user is connected or not ! \n    - Query that table to see if a user is active or not !\n    - Flow:\n       When a connection is established with a client server,\n        It writes to a new table \n\n        Available:\n        - userId\n        - status : available | un-available.\n\n    -   \n\n     ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
